                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="media-body p-2 mt-2">
                                <h3 class="heading mb-3">Spa Suites</h3>
                                <p>Each SPA care is the ultimate luxurious experience. The holistic philosophy of care, benefits both the soul and the mind, the face and the body. Enjoy revitalisation and regeneration of the skin.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
